description:
Experience Language Learning with LingQ — the natural and effective way to learn a new language.

LingQ is a language learning app that lets you grow your vocabulary and improve comprehension through meaningful exposure to the language with real content. 

Follow your interests and enjoy an immersive learning experience in over 50 languages. Learn Spanish, English, Japanese, Korean, Italian, German, Portuguese, French, Chinese, Arabic, and other languages.

Trusted by Learners Worldwide:
⭐ 4.7 star rating from over 45000 reviews.
⭐ Featured in CBC, Men’s Health, La Vanguardia, El País.

Designed for Real Language Learning

LingQ uses an input-based approach: you learn languages by reading and listening to real, interesting content at your level.

✅ Massive Content Library: Thousands of lessons from podcasts, books, interviews, videos, articles, and more — all with matching text for easy listening and reading.
✅ Follow Topics You Enjoy: Choose content you love and progress naturally through immersion, not drills.
✅ Import Your Favorite Content: Turn Netflix, YouTube, podcasts, books, and articles into personalized lessons.
✅ Powerful Reader: An effective, optimized reader that tracks every word you encounter to boost your vocabulary.
✅ Interactive Learning: Listen, read along, tap words for instant definitions, and learn naturally as you go.
✅ Advanced Progress Tracking: Monitor your listening, reading, study time, and vocabulary growth.
✅ Learn Anytime, Anywhere: Study offline and sync your progress automatically. Learn whenever you want.

✨ AI Language Learning Tools
• AI Audio Transcription: Turn podcasts and audiobooks into interactive lessons.
• AI Voices: Make your lessons, reviews, and chats more immersive with natural sounding text-to-speech voices.
• Advanced Chatbot: Get detailed tutor responses and real-time web search with our advanced Lynx AI Chatbot.
• AI-Simplified Lesson: Take advantage of more interesting content earlier on in your learning journey by generating simplified versions of lessons.

🎧 Read and Listen with Interactive Tools
• SRS vocabulary review for long-term retention;
• Mini Stories that build a strong foundation at any level;
• Grammar guides with clear, accessible explanations;
• Audio playlists for hands-free listening;
• Karaoke Mode to follow the text while listening;

🌍 A Global Community to Support You
• Writing Exchange for real corrections from native speakers;
• Tutoring sessions tailored to your goals;
• Community forum for questions, guidance, and motivation;
• Challenges that help you stay consistent and build strong habits;

📚Built by Language Learners
LingQ was co-founded by Steve Kaufmann, a polyglot who learned more than 20 languages using this same natural approach.

🌐 Learn Multiple Languages
LingQ supports more than 50 languages, including Spanish, English, Japanese, Korean, Italian, German, Portuguese, French, Chinese, Arabic and more.

🚀 Get LingQ Premium and Accelerate Your Learning
• Unlimited vocabulary lookup and SRS review;
• Comprehensive word tracking to boost your progress;
• Unlimited content imports;
• Access to AI features;

Start learning from real content. 
Download LingQ and begin today.

Visit www.lingq.com and discover a smarter way to learn languages.
